(514, 401, 'Testimonials - Homepage 1 (copy)', '', '<p>[pb_row background="none" border_width_value_="0" border_style="solid" border_color="#000" width_unit="%" div_padding_top="0" div_padding_right="0" div_padding_bottom="0" div_padding_left="0" css_suffix="jsn-testimonial-bg" ][pb_column span="span6"][pb_testimonial el_title="Testimonial 1" items_per_slide="1" slider_elements="indicator__#__ " content_elements="content__#__image__#__name__#__job_title__#__country__#__ " author_image_style="no-styling" content_type="words" appearing_animation="0" css_suffix="jsn-1st-testimonials" ][pb_testimonial_item elm_title="Robert Wilson" name="Robert Wilson" name_height="25" name_color="#000000" job_title="Performing Arts Journal, January 1993" country="" company="" web_url="http://" image_file="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2886/34224979806_4fe3bbc1f1_o_d.jpg" ]</p>\r\n<p>An artist recreates history, not like a historian, but as a poet. The artist takes the communal ideas and associations that surround the various gods of his or her time and plays with them, inventing another story for these mythic characters.</p>\r\n<p>[/pb_testimonial_item][pb_testimonial_item elm_title="Robert Wilson" name="Robert Wilson" name_height="25" name_color="#000000" job_title="Interview with John Bell, Theater Week, January 3, 1994" image_file="https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2813/34134489311_0c192222bf_o_d.jpg" ]</p>\r\n<p>Light is not an afterthought. Its something thats architectural, its structure, its thought about from the beginning, its part of the book, its like an actor. So its not a decoration.</p>\r\n<p>[/pb_testimonial_item][pb_testimonial_item elm_title="Robert Wilson" name="Robert Wilson" name_height="25" name_color="#000000" job_title="Dance Ink, 1995" image_file="https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4172/34224980176_683166afa2_o_d.jpg" ]</p>\r\n<p>Light in my work functions as a part of an architectural whole. It is an element that helps us hear and see, which is the primary way we communicate. Without light there is no space.</p>\r\n<p>[/pb_testimonial_item][/pb_testimonial][/pb_column][pb_column span="span6"][pb_module el_title="Testimonial of homepage1" module_name="474" module_alignment="left" module_show_title="no" appearing_animation="0" ][/pb_module][/pb_column][/pb_row]</p>', 1, 'content-bottom', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2017-04-26 15:55:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', -2, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{"prepare_content":"0","backgroundimage":"images\\/portrait.jpg","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static","module_tag":"div","bootstrap_size":"0","header_tag":"h3","header_class":"","style":"0"}', 0, '*');
